  "title": "Relates to prescription labels for gonadotropin-releasing hormone agonists, pubertal suppressants, anabolic steroids, alpha reductase inhibitors, progestins, or drug classes for hormone replacement therapy",
  "from_organization": "~{\"classification\": \"upper\"}",
